 to God&#39;s country”.</p><p> Longtime cast member <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kenan-thompson-questions-morgan-wallens-abrupt-snl-exit-what-are-you-trying-to-say-3850809">Kenan Thompson commented on the exit</a> , remarking: “I thought maybe he had to go to the potty or something” and adding: “I don&#39;t know what goes through people&#39;s minds when they decide to do stuff like that”.</p><p> Wallen has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-is-now-selling-merch-inspired-by-his-snl-walkoff-3851065">since made merchandise of his <em>SNL</em> walkoff.</a></p><p> It&#39;s the latest in a long list of controversies for the singer, including 2021 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radio-stations-and-playlists-drop-country-star-morgan-wallen-over-use-of-racial-slur-2871551">footage of him using a racial slur surfaced online</a> , causing him to be <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radio-stations-and-playlists-drop-country-star-morgan-wallen-over-use-of-racial-slur-2871551">dropped by a number of radio stations</a> as well as <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-dropped-by-big-loud-records-after-using-racial-slur-2872596">his record label, Big Loud</a> .尽管如此， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-sees-surge-album-sales-video-racial-slur-spread-online-2874316">他的专辑“危险”的销售额仍在激增</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-maintains-americas-no-1-album-two-weeks-after-racial-slur-video-2880492">，</a>沃伦在Billboard 200专辑排行榜上保持了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallens-dangerous-sets-new-country-album-record-weeks-on-from-racial-slur-2891205">纪录的十个星期</a>。沃伦（Wallen） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-tells-fans-not-to-defend-him-over-video-of-him-using-racial-slur-2877773">说，他的举动感到“尴尬和遗憾”</a> ，并要求球迷不要捍卫他。</p><p>在其他新闻中，10月，这位音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-dontates-500000-to-hurricane-helene-relief-effort-3798786">向美国红十字会捐赠了500,000美元，以支持Helen